sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant S as Vendedor
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant PI as Product&Inventory Service
    participant PIDB as PostgreSQL Product
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant C as Catalog Service
    participant CDB as MongoDB Catalog

    S->>G: POST /seller/products {name,desc,price,stock,category,images}
    G->>PI: Forward request autenticada
    PI->>PI: Validar ownership y campos obligatorios

    alt Datos válidos
        PI->>PIDB: Crear producto
        PIDB-->>PI: Producto persistido
        PI->>MQ: Publish ProductPublished
        PI-->>G: 201 Created + productId
        G-->>S: 201 Created

        MQ-->>C: ProductPublished
        C->>CDB: Upsert vista de lectura
        CDB-->>C: Vista actualizada
    else Datos inválidos
        PI-->>G: 400 Bad Request + errores
        G-->>S: 400 Bad Request
    end

    Note over PI,C: La propagacion Product -> Catalog es eventual y desacoplada.
